high_descs: move forward to the table
pick up the knife
turn to the other part of the table
slice the lettuce on the table
turn around to the fridge
drop the knife in the fridge
turn around to the table
pick up a slice of the lettuce
turn around to the fridge
place the lettuce to cool in the fridge and take it out
turn left and head to the sink
place the lettuce in the sink
anns.task_desc: place a cold lettuce slice in the sink

high_descs: Go to the left side of the kitchen island and face the yellow knife.
Pick up the yellow knife in front of you.
Go all the way around to the other side of the kitchen island.
Slice the lettuce that is in the middle of the counter.
Turn around and open the fridge behind you.
Put the knife in the fridge.
Turn around back to the counter.
Pick up a slice of lettuce.
Turn back around to the fridge.
Put the slice of lettuce in the fridge, close the door, wait, take the slice back out.
Take the slice of lettuce to the kitchen sink that is behind you to the left.
Put the slice of lettuce in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Cut a slice of lettuce, chill it and put it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn to the left, go to the wall, turn to the right, go forward to the counter of the left where the yellow handled knife is.
Pick up the yellow handled knife that is on the counter.
Turn to the left, go forward to the counter, turn to the right, go forward to the counter, turn to the right, go forward, turn to the counter on the right where the bread and lettuce is.
Use the knife to cut the lettuce into slices.
Turn to the right, go forward, turn to the right to face the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the knife inside, close the fridge.
Turn to the right, go forward, turn to the right to the counter where the sliced lettuce is.
Pick up a slice of lettuce from the counter.
Turn to the right, go forward, turn to the right to face the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the lettuce inside, close the door, remove the cold lettuce from the fridge, close the door.
Turn to the left, go forward to the counter, hang a right, go forward to the sink that is on the left.
Put the lettuce in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put cold lettuce in the sink.
